headline: Will Reaffirmed 2026 EPS Guidance and Stronger Medicaid Margins Change Centene’s (CNC) Narrative
summary: In recent weeks, Centene’s management met with investors and reaffirmed its 2026 earnings guidance, while highlighting improved profitability in its Medicaid operations and solid trends in Marketplace and Medicare businesses. Management also pointed to more than 40% expected growth in adjusted earnings per share for 2026, sharpening investor focus on the company’s margin improvement efforts across key segments.
